  <para style="h">Tito</para>
  <para style="toc1">Ebbaluwa ya Pawulo Omutukuvu eri Tito</para>
  <para style="toc2">Tito</para>
  <para style="toc3">Tit</para>
  <para style="mt2">Ebbaluwa ya Pawulo Omutukuvu eri</para>
  <para style="mt1">Tito</para>
  <para style="imt">Ennyanjula</para>
  <para style="ip">Ebbaluwa eno Pawulo Omutukuvu ye yagiwandiika ng’ali mu kibuga Nikopoli eky’omu Makedoniya. Yagiwandiika wakati wa <char style="sc">ad</char> 62 ne 67, ng’agiwandiikira muweereza munne Tito, gwe yali akoze naye mu biseera eby’obutume bwe ebyasooka. Yamuleka ku kizinga Kuleete ayambe okusitula Ekkanisa z’oku kizinga ekyo ng’azizzaamu amaanyi. Tito ye yali omulabirizi omubereberye ku kizinga Kuleete. Omulimu gwe yasookerako kwe kwawula abaweereza, n’okuyigiriza abakkiriza ebisookerwako ebikulu ebiri mu musingi gw’okukkiriza kwaffe. Pawulo yalaba nga kimusaanira okunnyonnyola ennyo ku bisaanyizo by’abo abaawulibwa okuba abaweereza mu Kkanisa era n’emirimu gyabwe nga bwe giri. Era n’akuutira Tito ku ebyo ebisaanira abakkiriza mu Kkanisa. Pawulo ayigiriza ku bizibu omuweereza wa Katonda by’asanga, era n’engeri gy’asobola okubivvuunuka.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:1">Bar 1:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 2:4">1Ti 2:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Pawulo omuweereza wa Katonda, era omutume wa Yesu Kristo ng’okukkiriza kw’abalonde ba Katonda bwe kuli n’okutegeera amazima agali mu kutya Katonda, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:2 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 1:1">2Ti 1:1</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 1:9">2Ti 1:9</ref></char></note>ebyesigamye ku kusuubira okw’obulamu obutaggwaawo, Katonda ow’amazima kwe yasuubiza ng’ebiro eby’emirembe n’emirembe tebinnabaawo, <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:3 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 2:6">1Ti 2:6</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 1:10">2Ti 1:10</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:11">1Ti 1:11</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">d </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 1:47">Luk 1:47</ref></char></note>naye mu ntuuko zaabyo, yayolesa ekigambo kye mu kubuulira Enjiri, kwe nateresebwa ng’ekiragiro kya Katonda Omulokozi waffe bwe kiri, <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 2:13">2Ko 2:13</ref></char></note>eri Tito omwana wange ddala ng’okukkiriza kwaffe ffenna okwa awamu bwe kuli, n’ekisa n’emirembe ebiva eri Katonda Kitaffe ne Kristo Yesu omulokozi waffe.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:5 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 27:7">Bik 27:7</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 11:30">Bik 11:30</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kyennava nkuleka mu Kuleete, olyoke otereeze ebyo ebyetaaga okutereeza, era otekewo n’abakadde<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">abakadde kitegeeza abantu abakulu mu kukkiriza abateekebwamu ekitiibwa abayinza okulondebwa ku nkiiko z’amakkanisa</char></note> b’ekkanisa mu buli kibuga, nga bwe nakulagira. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 3:2">1Ti 3:2</ref></char></note>Omuntu ateekwa okuba nga taliiko kya kunenyezebwa, nga musajja alina omukazi omu, era nga n’abaana baabwe bakkiriza, nga tebalina kibi kiyinza kuboogerwako era nga tebeenyigira mu bikolwa bya buseegu oba mu bujeemu. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:7 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 3:1">1Ti 3:1</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 4:1">1Ko 4:1</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 3:3">1Ti 3:3</ref>, <ref loc="1TI 3:8">8</ref></char></note>Omulabirizi kimugwanira okuba nga taliiko kya kunenyezebwa ng’omuwanika wa Katonda, nga si mukakanyavu, nga si wa busungu, nga si mutamiivu, nga si mukambwe, nga teyeegomba kufuna magoba mu bukuusa <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:8 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 3:2">1Ti 3:2</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 3:3">2Ti 3:3</ref></char></note>naye ayaniriza abagenyi, ayagala okukola obulungi, omutegeevu, nga mwenkanya, nga mutukuvu, era ng’amanyi okwefuga. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:9 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:19">1Ti 1:19</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:10">1Ti 1:10</ref></char></note>Ateekwa okuba omuntu anywerera ku kigambo ekyesigwa, alyoke asobole okunnyonnyola abantu enjigiriza entuufu, n’okulaga obukyamu bw’abo abagiwakanya.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:10 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 1:6">1Ti 1:6</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 11:2">Bik 11:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kubanga waliwo bangi abawakana, aboogera ebitaliimu era abalimba, n’okusingira ddala abo ab’omu bakomole. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 3:6">2Ti 3:6</ref></char></note>Basaanye okusirisibwa, kubanga boonoona buli maka, nga bayigiriza ebitabagwanidde, balyoke beefunire amagoba ag’obukuusa. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:12 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 17:28">Bik 17:28</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 2:11">Bik 2:11</ref></char></note>Omu ku bo, nnabbi waabwe bo kyeyava agamba nti, “Abakuleete balimba bulijjo, z’ensolo enkambwe, era ba mululu ate bagayaavu.” <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:13 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 13:10">2Ko 13:10</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="TIT 2:2">Tit 2:2</ref></char></note>Kye yagamba kya mazima. Noolwekyo oteekwa okubanenya n’amaanyi kiryoke kibaleetere okukkiriza okutuufu, <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:14 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:4">1Ti 1:4</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 2:22">Bak 2:22</ref></char></note>balekeraawo okuwuliriza enfumo ez’Ekiyudaaya, n’ebiragiro abantu abakyama okuva ku mazima bye bagunja. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 14:14">Bar 14:14</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 14:23">23</ref></char></note>Eri abalongoofu, ebintu byonna biba birongoofu, naye eri abo abatali balongoofu n’abatakkiriza, tewaba kirongoofu na kimu. Kubanga amagezi gaabwe n’ebirowoozo byabwe byayonooneka. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 2:4">1Yk 2:4</ref></char></note>Bagamba nti bamanyi Katonda, naye mu bikolwa byabwe bamwegaana. Bagwenyufu era bajeemu, tebasaanira kuweebwa mulimu mulungi n’akatono.</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Enjigiriza Entuufu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 1:10">1Ti 1:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Naye ggwe yogeranga ebyo ebitayawukana na njigiriza entuufu. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="TIT 1:13">Tit 1:13</ref></char></note>Kubirizanga abasajja abakulu babe bateefu, abassibwamu ekitiibwa, abeegendereza, abajjudde okukkiriza, okwagala n’okugumiikiriza.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 3:8">1Ti 3:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Abakazi abakulu nabo bakubirize bw’otyo babe n’empisa ezisaanira abantu ba Katonda, nga tebawaayiriza, era nga tebatamiira, wabula nga bayigiriza ebirungi, <verse number="4" style="v"/>balyoke basobole okugunjula abakazi abato okwagalanga ba bbaabwe awamu n’abaana baabwe. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:5 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 5:22">Bef 5:22</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 6:1">1Ti 6:1</ref></char></note>Era babenga beegendereza, era abalongoofu, era abakola obulungi emirimu mu maka gaabwe, era abawulize eri ba bbaabwe, ekigambo kya Katonda kiremenga okuvvoolebwa.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 5:1">1Ti 5:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>N’abavubuka bakubirizenga babe beegendereza, <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 4:12">1Ti 4:12</ref></char></note>mu bintu byonna, ng’obeera ekyokulabirako ekirungi mu byonna by’okola, ng’oli mwesimbu era assaayo omwoyo mu kuyigiriza kwo. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1PE 2:12">1Pe 2:12</ref></char></note>Buli ky’oyogera kiteekwa okuba nga tekiriiko kya kunenyezebwa, oyo awakanya alyoke aswale, nga talina kibi kya kukwogerako.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 6:5">Bef 6:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Era kubirizanga abaddu bawulirenga bakama baabwe era babagonderenga mu byonna, nga tebabawakanya, <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 5:16">Mat 5:16</ref></char></note>wadde okubabbangako ebyabwe. Wabula babenga beesigwa ddala mu byonna, nga beeyisa bulungi, abantu balyoke bayaayaanire okuyigiriza kwa Katonda Omulokozi waffe mu buli ngeri yonna.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 2:4">1Ti 2:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kubanga ekisa kya Katonda ekireetera abantu bonna obulokozi kirabise, <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:12 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="TIT 3:3">Tit 3:3</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 3:12">2Ti 3:12</ref></char></note>era kituyigiriza tuleke obutatya Katonda, n’okwegomba kw’ensi, tulyoke tube beegendereza, abatuukirivu abatya Katonda nga tuli mu mulembe gwa kaakano; <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 1:1">2Pe 1:1</ref></char></note>nga tulindirira olunaku lwe tusuubira, n’okulabika kw’ekitiibwa kya Katonda omukulu era Omulokozi waffe Yesu Kristo; <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:14 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 19:5">Kuv 19:5</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 2:10">Bef 2:10</ref></char></note>eyeewaayo ku lwaffe, alyoke atununule mu bujeemu bwaffe bwonna, era yeerongooseza eggwanga ery’envuma, erinyiikirira ebikolwa ebirungi. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Ebyo by’obanga oyigiriza abantu. Buuliriranga era nenyanga n’obuyinza bwonna. Omuntu yenna takunyoomanga.</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Okuwabula abakkiriza</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:1 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 13:1">Bar 13:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2TI 2:21">2Ti 2:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ebintu ebyo bijjukizenga abafuzi n’ab’obuyinza, babiwulirenga, era babigonderenga, era babenga beetegefu okukola buli mulimu omulungi. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 4:31">Bef 4:31</ref>; <ref loc="2TI 2:24">2Ti 2:24</ref></char></note>Bakuutire baleme kwogerebwako bubi, era beewalenga okuyomba, babenga bakkakkamu era babeerenga bawombeefu eri abantu bonna.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Kubanga naffe ffennyini twali basirusiru era abajeemu, nga tuwabye, era nga tufugibwa okwegomba kwaffe okubi, n’amasanyu aga buli ngeri, nga tuli ba ttima era ab’obuggya, nga tukyayibwa era nga tukyawagana. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:4 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 2:7">Bef 2:7</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="TIT 2:11">Tit 2:11</ref></char></note>Naye ekisa kya Katonda Omulokozi waffe n’okwagala kwe bwe byalabika, <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:5 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 2:9">Bef 2:9</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 12:2">Bar 12:2</ref></char></note>n’atulokola, si lwa bikolwa eby’omu butuukirivu bye twakola, wabula olw’okusaasira kwe mu kunaazibwa okw’okuzaalibwa okw’omulundi ogwokubiri n’okufuulibwa abaggya olwa Mwoyo Mutukuvu, <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 5:5">Bar 5:5</ref></char></note>gwe yatuyiwako mu bungi ku lwa Yesu Kristo Omulokozi waffe. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:7 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 3:24">Bar 3:24</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:17">Bar 8:17</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:24">Bar 8:24</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">d </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="TIT 1:2">Tit 1:2</ref></char></note>Bwe tulimala okutukuzibwa olw’ekisa kye, tulyoke tufune omugabo mu kusuubira obulamu obutaggwaawo. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:8 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:15">1Ti 1:15</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="TIT 2:14">Tit 2:14</ref></char></note>Ekigambo ekyo kyesigwa, era nkukuutira ebyo obinywezenga abakkiriza Katonda bajjukirenga okukola ebikolwa ebirungi; ebintu ebyo birungi era bigasa abantu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 1:4">1Ti 1:4</ref>; <ref loc="2TI 2:14">2Ti 2:14</ref></char>
    </note>Naye weewalenga empaka ez’obusirusiru, n’okukaayana ku nkalala eziraga obuzaale bw’abantu, n’ennyombo, n’entalo ebikwata ku mateeka; kubanga tebiriiko kye bigasa era tebiriimu nsa. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 16:17">Bar 16:17</ref></char></note>Omuntu ayawulayawula mu bantu bw’omalanga okumulabula omulundi ogusooka, era n’ogwokubiri, omwewalanga, <verse number="11" style="v"/>kubanga omuntu ng’oyo aba amaze okukyamizibwa mu kibi, era nga yeesalira yekka omusango.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:12 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 20:4">Bik 20:4</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2TI 4:9">2Ti 4:9</ref>, <ref loc="2TI 4:21">21</ref></char>
    </note>Bwe nkutumiranga Atema oba Tukiko, oyanguwanga okujja gye ndi mu Nikopoli, kubanga nsazeewo okubeera eyo mu biseera eby’obutiti. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 18:24">Bik 18:24</ref></char></note>Fuba okusibirira Zeena munnamateeka ne Apolo obatume babe nga tebaliiko kye beetaaga.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">nny 8</char>
    </note>Era kubiriza abantu baffe bayige okukolanga emirimu omuva ebyetaagibwa, balemenga kubeera awo nga tebaliiko kye bagasa.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 1:2">1Ti 1:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Bonna abali nange bakulamusizza.</para>
  <para style="p">Olamuse abo bonna abatwagala mu kukkiriza.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">Ekisa kibeerenga nammwe mwenna.</para>
</usx>
